'''Tafelwit tawalant''' d amsasa afelwan i [[aferdis akruran|yiferdisen ikruranen]], ttwasnin s unect n [[Uṭṭun abelkim|wuṭṭun-nsen abelkim]], [[tawila taliktṛunant]] d iylanen ikruranen imallusen, anda tamuska-ines tesskanay-d ''tizniwin tiwalanin''. S umata, iferdisen i d-yezgan deg wedras amezwaru ttilin ([[tallit n tfelwit tawalant|tallit]]) d [[Asin|amɣuz]] ɣer tnila n uzelmaḍ, U d [[arasi|aramɣuz]] ɣer tnila n uyeffus, anda i ttmersen iferdisen ilan (yesɛan) tikliwin tikruranin timarwasin (yemcabin) deg yiwen n wejgu. Idrasen n tfelwit ttusemman (di tuget n tugnatin) s [[tallit n tfelwit tawalant|twalanin]], ma d ijga ttusemman s [[tagrawt n tfelwit tawalant|tegrawin]]. Yerna 6 n tegrawin lant (sɛant) ismawen s tmerniwt ɣer wuṭṭunen usligen. Amedya, iferdisen n tegrawt tis 17 igan d [[Halujin|ihalujinen]], d tegrawt tis 18 igan d [[agaz aheggaṛ|igazen iheggaṛen]], akken i d-ittwafsar deg telɣa n kuẓ n yideggan usrimen neɣ deg [[amegganu n tfelwit tawalant|yiswiren ifurkanen]] yeqqnen s tčarit n [[amezzay abelkan|imezzayen ibelkamen]] yemgaraden.

Yella wamek ara ad tettwasuddes tfelwit tawalant i usuddem n wassaɣen gar n yiylanen n yiferdisen yemgaraden, yakk d d yiylanen d teklatin tikruranin yettuṛajun i yiferdisen ur d-nettwasnirem ara neɣ wid i d-ittwasuddsen s akken kan. Amusnaw n [[takrura|tekrura]] n [[Rusya]] [[Dmitri Mandelyiv]] yella d netta i d amdan amezwaru ifser-d tafelwit tawalant deg useggas n [[1869]], sin akin yella-d usnerni-ines s talɣa tagejdant i usegzi n tniliwin tiwalanin i yiferdisen yettwassnen imir-nni. Akken i icuyel kra n yiylanen [[iferdisen n Mandelyiv ittucuylen|iferdisen ur nettwafran ara]] i yellan yettuṛaju ad ččaren ibeṛjujen n tfelwit. Dɣa yella-d usihrew n tekti n Mandelyiv u tettusenṭeḍ yakked [[asnirem n yiferdisen ikruranen|usnirem d usnulfu n yiferdisen imaynuten]] niḍen d usnerni n tmudmiwin tiẓranin timatuyin i usegzi n tkelli takrurant.<br/>
Tafelwit tawalant tatrart tettak-d akatar yelhan i teslaḍt n [[tasefmirt takrurant|tsedmirin tikruranin]], yerna mazal-itt tettusexdem s waṭas di [[Takrura|tekrura]] d [[tafizikt taɣisant|tfizikt taɣisant]] d tussniwin niḍen.

